---
title: Crispy Chicken Parmigiana Salad with Potatoes and Spinach
description: Everyone knows the best part of Chicken Parmigiana is the layer of crispy cheese on top of chicken. We’re recreating that same combination, but lightening it up in salad form. We think it’s the most delicious way to get in those leafy greens!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/crispy-chicken-parmigiana-salad-1b6fe702.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ca/recipecards/card/crispy-chicken-parmigiana-salad-8c71daa3.pdf
